{"tid":2445899,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★老綜又贏！陳茂波：面對財赤，政府沒有減少社會福利的撥款！","createTime":"2021-03-14T04:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T04:27:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a83a78072d531176b8424b21a274b5b4b67652e3","tid":2445899,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"陳茂波在本台英文節目《給香港的信》表示，現時並非調整薪俸稅及利得稅的時候，因此沒有調高有關稅率，而且繼續提供100%寬減，各以1萬元為上限。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，本港新冠疫苗接種計劃已展開，希望能控制疫情，商業活動得以恢復，期望下半年經濟有較強復蘇動力。陳茂波說，會繼續投資在有巨大發展潛力的行業，尤其是金融服務及創科行業，推廣綠色及可持續金融，保持金融業的活力。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳茂波又提到，面對財赤，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>政府沒有減少在教育、社會福利及健康護理的撥款</strong></span>，而是減少經營開支，落實公務員編制零增長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580473-20210314.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580473-20210314.htm&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfFiy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=807b1ef7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580473-20210314.htm&h=81401e10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580473-20210314.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5e797aae7ce77432e3aeaf14db204aea2b510184","tid":2445899,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"老綜加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f76767d735ee35bb9c711f8cc3b96901c739a3","tid":2445899,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdkW2LH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdkW2LH.png&h=4e75bbfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dba415bce0c49da5e7abf68c60e630c35a35246e"